{"sequence":54,"timestamp":"2026-04-17T20:15:38.167131077Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-ab07ff12","body":"finding_summary: `build_mock_br_adapter()` scripts a single happy-path exchange instead of mirroring the staged bead graph. The returned fixture only has one initial `show` response (`PREPARE_TASK_ID`), then a synthetic follow-up `show`, and the synthetic bead stays `open` even after the mocked `close` because no later `show`/`list` state is updated. Any integration test that inspects `ROOT_EPIC_ID` or `VALIDATE_TASK_ID`, re-reads the created bead, or validates post-close state will either exhaust the queue or observe impossible data. affected_files: [\"src/test_support/e2e_fixtures.rs:318\", \"src/test_support/e2e_fixtures.rs:325\", \"src/test_support/e2e_fixtures.rs:343\"] remediation_hint: Make the fixture's `MockBrAdapter` stateful, or queue enough per-command responses so every staged bead can be shown and post-`create`/`close` reads reflect the created/closed state.","dedup_key":"5dc30845f52e89029611a941566106a33298a3c0cdd2d7a5773c6d68c8456dce","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260417184955","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":55,"timestamp":"2026-04-17T20:15:38.177106708Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-96eb17b8","body":"finding_summary: The new smoke test enforces a strict one-second wall-clock budget around real filesystem work. That makes the test sensitive to host load and sandbox performance, so it can fail spuriously on slower CI or Nix builders even when the fixture is functionally correct. affected_files: [\"src/test_support/e2e_fixtures.rs:462\"] remediation_hint: Keep the fixture fast, but move the runtime budget to a benchmark/ignored perf test or replace the hard deadline with a much looser non-flaky assertion.","dedup_key":"b113c174a164e7d943a0c66b9bc7d7807d16c646685869035f0eff9c324bad8d","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260417184955","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
